{"id":35209,"date":"2021-02-11T12:09:39","date_gmt":"2021-02-11T08:09:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=35209"},"modified":"2021-02-11T12:09:39","modified_gmt":"2021-02-11T08:09:39","slug":"prophet-performs-miracles","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/11\/prophet-performs-miracles\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet performs signs for his companions"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: We were on a journey with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and we ran short of water. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Bring the remaining water.<\/strong>\u201d They brought a vessel with a little water in it. The Prophet placed his hands in the vessel, then he said, \u201c<strong>Come to the blessed purification, a blessing from Allah<\/strong>.\u201d I saw the water emanating from between the Prophet\u2019s fingers, and we heard his food glorifying Allah as he ate it.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3579<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0631\u064d \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e <strong>\u0627\u0637\u0652\u0644\u064f\u0628\u064f\u064